---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout
  title="Ředitelka | Domov Turovice"
  description="Mgr. Zina Filip Dadlíková, DiS. — ředitelka Domova Turovice s 22 lety praxe v péči o seniory a osoby s demencí."
>

<style>
.section-label {
  display: block;
  font-size: var(--font-size-label);
  font-weight: 700;
  letter-spacing: .12em;
  text-transform: uppercase;
  color: var(--clr-primary);
  margin-bottom: 14px;
}
.section-intro {
  font-size: 1.05rem;
  line-height: 1.7;
  color: var(--clr-text);
  max-width: 700px;
  margin: 0 0 40px;
}

/* ── DIRECTOR HERO ── */
.director-hero {
  padding: 72px 0 64px;
  background: var(--clr-bg);
}
.director-hero-inner {
  display: grid;
  grid-template-columns: 260px 1fr;
  gap: 56px;
  align-items: start;
}
.director-photo {
  width: 220px; height: 260px;
  border-radius: 16px;
  overflow: hidden;
  background: var(--clr-bg-alt);
  border: 1.5px solid var(--clr-border);
}
.director-photo-placeholder {
  width: 100%; height: 100%;
  display: flex;
  flex-direction: column;
  align-items: center;
  justify-content: center;
  gap: 12px;
  color: var(--clr-muted);
  font-size: var(--font-size-meta);
  text-align: center;
  padding: 16px;
}
.director-photo-placeholder svg { width: 56px; height: 56px; fill: var(--clr-border); }
.director-badge {
  margin-top: 12px;
  background: var(--clr-primary);
  color: #fff;
  border-radius: 8px;
  font-size: var(--font-size-meta);
  font-weight: 700;
  padding: 8px 14px;
  text-align: center;
  width: 220px;
}
.director-intro h1 {
  font-family: var(--ff-head);
  font-size: clamp(1.7rem, 3.5vw, 2.3rem);
  font-weight: 700;
  color: var(--clr-heading);
  margin: 8px 0 6px;
  line-height: 1.25;
}
.director-title {
  font-size: var(--font-size-small);
  color: var(--clr-muted);
  font-weight: 600;
  margin: 0 0 20px;
}
.director-perex {
  font-size: var(--font-size-small);
  line-height: 1.75;
  color: var(--clr-text);
  margin: 0 0 24px;
  max-width: 600px;
}
.director-contacts { display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 10px; margin-bottom: 28px; }
.contact-row {
  display: flex;
  align-items: center;
  gap: 10px;
  font-size: var(--font-size-small);
  color: var(--clr-text);
}
.contact-row svg {
  width: 18px; height: 18px;
  fill: var(--clr-primary);
  flex-shrink: 0;
}
.contact-row a { color: var(--clr-primary); font-weight: 600; text-decoration: none; }
.contact-row a:hover { text-decoration: underline; }
.director-cta-row { display: flex; gap: 14px; flex-wrap: wrap; }
.btn {
  display: inline-flex;
  align-items: center;
  gap: 8px;
  padding: 12px 22px;
  border-radius: 8px;
  font-weight: 700;
  font-size: var(--font-size-small);
  text-decoration: none;
  transition: all .2s;
}
.btn-primary { background: var(--clr-primary); color: #fff; border: 2px solid var(--clr-primary); }
.btn-primary:hover { background: #7a3238; border-color: #7a3238; }
.btn-secondary { background: #fff; color: var(--clr-primary); border: 2px solid var(--clr-primary); }
.btn-secondary:hover { background: var(--clr-primary); color: #fff; }

/* ── STATS STRIP ── */
.stats-strip { background: var(--clr-primary); padding: 40px 0; }
.stats-grid {
  display: grid;
  grid-template-columns: repeat(4, 1fr);
  gap: 32px;
}
.stat-item { text-align: center; }
.stat-number {
  display: block;
  font-family: var(--ff-head);
  font-size: 2.4rem;
  font-weight: 700;
  color: #fff;
  line-height: 1;
  margin-bottom: 8px;
}
.stat-label {
  font-size: var(--font-size-meta);
  color: rgba(255,255,255,.8);
  line-height: 1.45;
}

/* ── PROFILE SECTION ── */
.profile-section { padding: 72px 0; background: #fff; }
.profile-section h2 {
  font-family: var(--ff-head);
  font-size: clamp(1.6rem, 3vw, 2rem);
  font-weight: 700;
  color: var(--clr-heading);
  margin: 0 0 12px;
}
.profile-grid {
  display: grid;
  grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr);
  gap: 24px;
}
.profile-card {
  background: var(--clr-bg-alt);
  border: 1.5px solid var(--clr-border);
  border-radius: 14px;
  padding: 28px 24px;
  border-top: 4px solid var(--clr-primary);
}
.profile-card-icon {
  width: 48px; height: 48px;
  border-radius: 10px;
  display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center;
  margin-bottom: 16px;
}
.profile-card-icon svg { width: 26px; height: 26px; }
.profile-card h3 {
  font-family: var(--ff-head);
  font-size: 1.05rem;
  font-weight: 700;
  color: var(--clr-heading);
  margin: 0 0 10px;
}
.profile-card p { font-size: var(--font-size-base); line-height: 1.7; color: var(--clr-text); margin: 0; }

/* ── QUOTE ── */
.quote-section { padding: 64px 0; background: var(--clr-bg); }
.quote-inner {
  max-width: 720px;
  position: relative;
  padding-left: 60px;
}
.quote-mark {
  position: absolute;
  left: 0; top: -20px;
  font-family: var(--ff-head);
  font-size: 8rem;
  color: rgba(155,66,73,.15);
  line-height: 1;
  pointer-events: none;
}
blockquote {
  font-family: var(--ff-head);
  font-size: clamp(1.1rem, 2.5vw, 1.4rem);
  font-style: italic;
  color: var(--clr-heading);
  line-height: 1.65;
  margin: 0 0 20px;
}
.quote-author {
  font-size: var(--font-size-caption);
  font-weight: 700;
  color: var(--clr-primary);
  margin: 0;
}

/* ── EDUCATION ── */
.edu-section { padding: 72px 0; background: #fff; }
.edu-section h2 {
  font-family: var(--ff-head);
  font-size: clamp(1.5rem, 3vw, 2rem);
  font-weight: 700;
  color: var(--clr-heading);
  margin: 0 0 12px;
}
.edu-grid {
  display: grid;
  grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
  gap: 48px;
  margin-top: 40px;
}
.edu-block h3 {
  font-family: var(--ff-head);
  font-size: 1.1rem;
  font-weight: 700;
  color: var(--clr-heading);
  margin: 0 0 20px;
  padding-bottom: 12px;
  border-bottom: 1.5px solid var(--clr-border);
}
.edu-list { list-style: none; margin: 0; padding: 0; display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 0; }
.edu-list li { display: flex; gap: 14px; align-items: flex-start; padding: 16px 0; border-bottom: 1px solid var(--clr-border); }
.edu-list li:last-child { border-bottom: none; }
.edu-dot {
  flex-shrink: 0;
  width: 12px; height: 12px;
  border-radius: 50%;
  background: var(--clr-primary);
  margin-top: 5px;
}
.edu-degree {
  font-weight: 700;
  font-size: var(--font-size-small);
  color: var(--clr-heading);
  margin-bottom: 3px;
}
.edu-school { font-size: var(--font-size-meta); color: var(--clr-muted); }

.cert-list { list-style: none; margin: 0; padding: 0; display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 0; }
.cert-list li {
  padding: 12px 0;
  border-bottom: 1px solid var(--clr-border);
  font-size: var(--font-size-small);
  color: var(--clr-text);
  display: flex;
  align-items: center;
  gap: 10px;
}
.cert-list li:last-child { border-bottom: none; }
.cert-list li::before {
  content: '';
  flex-shrink: 0;
  width: 8px; height: 8px;
  border-radius: 50%;
  background: var(--clr-green);
}

/* ── SKILLS ── */
.skills-section { padding: 72px 0; background: var(--clr-bg); }
.skills-section h2 {
  font-family: var(--ff-head);
  font-size: clamp(1.5rem, 3vw, 2rem);
  font-weight: 700;
  color: var(--clr-heading);
  margin: 0 0 12px;
}
.skills-grid {
  display: grid;
  grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
  gap: 28px;
  margin-top: 40px;
}
.skills-card {
  background: #fff;
  border: 1.5px solid var(--clr-border);
  border-top: 4px solid var(--clr-primary);
  border-radius: 14px;
  padding: 28px 24px;
}
.skills-card h3 {
  font-family: var(--ff-head);
  font-size: 1.05rem;
  font-weight: 700;
  color: var(--clr-heading);
  margin: 0 0 18px;
}
.skill-tag-list { display: flex; flex-wrap: wrap; gap: 8px; }
.skill-tag {
  display: inline-block;
  background: rgba(155,66,73,.09);
  color: var(--clr-primary);
  border-radius: 20px;
  font-size: var(--font-size-meta);
  font-weight: 600;
  padding: 5px 12px;
}
.skill-tag.green { background: rgba(89,152,108,.09); color: var(--clr-green); }

/* ── CTA ── */
.cta-section {
  padding: 72px 0;
  background: #EDE8E3;
}
.cta-inner {
  text-align: center;
  max-width: 600px;
  margin: 0 auto;
  color: var(--clr-primary);
}
.cta-inner .section-label { color: var(--clr-primary); }
.cta-inner h2 {
  font-family: var(--ff-head);
  font-size: clamp(1.7rem, 3.5vw, 2.3rem);
  font-weight: 700;
  color: var(--clr-primary);
  margin: 14px 0;
}
.cta-inner p { font-size: 1.05rem; line-height: 1.65; color: var(--clr-text-body); margin: 0 0 32px; }
.cta-buttons { display: flex; gap: 14px; justify-content: center; flex-wrap: wrap; }
.cta-buttons .btn {
  display: inline-flex;
  align-items: center;
  gap: 8px;
  padding: 13px 24px;
}
.btn-cta-main { background: #fff; color: var(--clr-primary); border: 2px solid #fff; }
.btn-cta-main:hover { background: transparent; color: #fff; }
.btn-cta-sec { background: transparent; color: #fff; border: 2px solid rgba(255,255,255,.6); }
.btn-cta-sec:hover { border-color: #fff; background: rgba(255,255,255,.12); }

/* ── RESPONSIVE ── */
@media (max-width: 900px) {
  .director-hero-inner { grid-template-columns: 1fr; gap: 32px; }
  .stats-grid { grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr); }
  .profile-grid, .edu-grid, .skills-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
}
@media (max-width: 640px) {
  .director-hero { padding: 48px 0 40px; }
  .stats-strip { padding: 28px 0; }
  .quote-inner { padding-left: 0; }
  .quote-mark { display: none; }
}

.related-links { padding: 56px 0; background: var(--clr-bg); }
.related-links h2 {
  font-family: var(--ff-head);
  font-size: 1.4rem;
  font-weight: 700;
  color: var(--clr-heading);
  margin: 0 0 24px;
}
.related-grid {
  display: grid;
  grid-template-columns: repeat(4, 1fr);
  gap: 14px;
}
.related-item {
  display: flex;
  align-items: center;
  gap: 12px;
  padding: 16px 18px;
  background: #fff;
  border: 1.5px solid var(--clr-border);
  border-radius: 10px;
  text-decoration: none;
  color: var(--clr-heading);
  font-weight: 600;
  font-size: var(--font-size-ui);
  transition: all .2s;
}
.related-item:hover { border-color: var(--clr-primary); color: var(--clr-primary); box-shadow: 0 4px 14px rgba(155,66,73,.1); }
.related-item svg {
  width: 20px; height: 20px;
  stroke: var(--clr-primary);
  fill: none;
  stroke-width: 2;
  stroke-linecap: round;
  stroke-linejoin: round;
  flex-shrink: 0;
}
@media (max-width: 768px) { .related-grid { grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr); } }
@media (max-width: 480px) { .related-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; } }

</style>

<div class="page-content">

  <!-- DIRECTOR HERO -->
  <section class="director-hero">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="director-hero-inner">

        <div class="director-photo-wrap">
          <div class="director-photo">
            <div class="director-photo-placeholder">
              <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path d="M12 12c2.7 0 4.8-2.1 4.8-4.8S14.7 2.4 12 2.4 7.2 4.5 7.2 7.2 9.3 12 12 12zm0 2.4c-3.2 0-9.6 1.6-9.6 4.8v2.4h19.2v-2.4c0-3.2-6.4-4.8-9.6-4.8z"/></svg>
              <span>Fotografie bude doplněna</span>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="director-badge">Ředitelka Domova Turovice</div>
        </div>

        <div class="director-intro">
          <span class="section-label">Vedení domova</span>
          <h1>Mgr. Zina Filip Dadlíková, DiS.</h1>
          <p class="director-title">Ředitelka · Odbornice v sociálních službách</p>
          <p class="director-perex">
            Domov Turovice vede zkušená manažerka a sociální pracovnice s <strong>22 lety praxe</strong> v přímé práci s klienty. Zina Filip Dadlíková stojí za odbornou koncepcí péče od samého počátku — ještě dříve, než vznikl samotný domov. Její vize se stala základem, na kterém celý projekt vyrostl.
          </p>
          <div class="director-contacts">
            <div class="contact-row">
              <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path d="M6.62 10.79c1.44 2.83 3.76 5.14 6.59 6.59l2.2-2.2c.27-.27.67-.36 1.02-.24 1.12.37 2.33.57 3.57.57.55 0 1 .45 1 1V20c0 .55-.45 1-1 1-9.39 0-17-7.61-17-17 0-.55.45-1 1-1h3.5c.55 0 1 .45 1 1 0 1.25.2 2.45.57 3.57.11.35.03.74-.25 1.02l-2.2 2.2z"/></svg>
              <span>Kancelář: <a href="tel:+420588003888">+420 588 003 888</a></span>
            </div>
            <div class="contact-row">
              <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path d="M6.62 10.79c1.44 2.83 3.76 5.14 6.59 6.59l2.2-2.2c.27-.27.67-.36 1.02-.24 1.12.37 2.33.57 3.57.57.55 0 1 .45 1 1V20c0 .55-.45 1-1 1-9.39 0-17-7.61-17-17 0-.55.45-1 1-1h3.5c.55 0 1 .45 1 1 0 1.25.2 2.45.57 3.57.11.35.03.74-.25 1.02l-2.2 2.2z"/></svg>
              <span>Mobil: <a href="tel:+420724211589">+420 724 211 589</a></span>
            </div>
            <div class="contact-row">
              <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path d="M20 4H4c-1.1 0-2 .9-2 2v12c0 1.1.9 2 2 2h16c1.1 0 2-.9 2-2V6c0-1.1-.9-2-2-2zm0 4l-8 5-8-5V6l8 5 8-5v2z"/></svg>
              <span><a href="mailto:reditelka@domovturovice.cz">reditelka@domovturovice.cz</a></span>
            </div>
            <div class="contact-row">
              <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path d="M12 2C8.13 2 5 5.13 5 9c0 5.25 7 13 7 13s7-7.75 7-13c0-3.87-3.13-7-7-7zm0 9.5c-1.38 0-2.5-1.12-2.5-2.5s1.12-2.5 2.5-2.5 2.5 1.12 2.5 2.5-1.12 2.5-2.5 2.5z"/></svg>
              <span>Turovice 104, 751 14 Turovice — kancelář v budově C, 1. nadpodlaží</span>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="director-cta-row">
            <a href="mailto:reditelka@domovturovice.cz" class="btn btn-primary">Napište ředitelce</a>
            <a href="/kontakt" class="btn btn-secondary">Kontakt a prohlídka</a>
          </div>
        </div>

      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- STATISTIKY -->
  <div class="stats-strip">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="stats-grid">
        <div class="stat-item">
          <span class="stat-number">22</span>
          <span class="stat-label">let v přímé práci s klienty</span>
        </div>
        <div class="stat-item">
          <span class="stat-number">2017</span>
          <span class="stat-label">rok, kdy stála za odbornou koncepcí domova</span>
        </div>
        <div class="stat-item">
          <span class="stat-number">6</span>
          <span class="stat-label">specializací v péči o seniory a osoby s demencí</span>
        </div>
        <div class="stat-item">
          <span class="stat-number">104</span>
          <span class="stat-label">míst v domově, za jehož kvalitu péče ručí</span>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- PROFIL -->
  <section class="profile-section">
    <div class="container">
      <span class="section-label">Odborný profil</span>
      <h2>Zkušenost, která přináší klid vám i vašemu blízkému</h2>
      <p class="section-intro">Celých 22 let pracovala Zina Filip Dadlíková přímo s klienty — seniory i lidmi s demencí. Řídila aktivizační programy, plánovala individuální péči a podporovala rodiny v těžkých chvílích. Teprve na základě této hluboké zkušenosti se stala ředitelkou Domova Turovice.</p>

      <div class="profile-grid">
        <div class="profile-card">
          <div class="profile-card-icon" style="background:rgba(155,66,73,.1)">
            <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" style="fill:var(--clr-primary)"><path d="M12 2C8.13 2 5 5.13 5 9c0 3.54 2.29 6.53 5.47 7.59.4.07.55-.17.55-.38 0-.19-.01-.82-.01-1.49-2.01.37-2.53-.49-2.69-.94-.09-.23-.48-.94-.82-1.13-.28-.15-.68-.52-.01-.53.63-.01 1.08.58 1.23.82.72 1.21 1.87.87 2.33.66.07-.52.28-.87.51-1.07-1.78-.2-3.64-.89-3.64-3.95 0-.87.31-1.59.82-2.15-.08-.2-.36-1.02.08-2.12 0 0 .67-.21 2.2.82.64-.18 1.32-.27 2-.27.68 0 1.36.09 2 .27 1.53-1.04 2.2-.82 2.2-.82.44 1.1.16 1.92.08 2.12.51.56.82 1.27.82 2.15 0 3.07-1.87 3.75-3.65 3.95.29.25.54.73.54 1.48 0 1.07-.01 1.93-.01 2.2 0 .21.15.46.55.38A8.012 8.012 0 0 0 19 9c0-3.87-3.13-7-7-7z"/></svg>
          </div>
          <h3>Péče a podpora klientů</h3>
          <p>Dvacet dva let pracovala přímo s klienty — seniory a osoby se sníženou soběstačností. Zajišťovala jejich podporu v každodenních činnostech a metodicky vedla proces adaptace v zařízení.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="profile-card">
          <div class="profile-card-icon" style="background:rgba(89,152,108,.1)">
            <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" style="fill:var(--clr-green)"><path d="M19 3H5c-1.1 0-2 .9-2 2v14c0 1.1.9 2 2 2h14c1.1 0 2-.9 2-2V5c0-1.1-.9-2-2-2zm-7 3c1.93 0 3.5 1.57 3.5 3.5S13.93 13 12 13s-3.5-1.57-3.5-3.5S10.07 6 12 6zm7 13H5v-.23c0-.62.28-1.2.76-1.58C7.47 15.82 9.64 15 12 15s4.53.82 6.24 2.19c.48.38.76.97.76 1.58V19z"/></svg>
          </div>
          <h3>Individuální plánování a odborná činnost</h3>
          <p>Realizovala individuální plánování služeb a vedla komplexní dokumentaci. Koordinovala spolupráci s lékaři, terapeuty a dalšími odborníky tak, aby péče skutečně odpovídala potřebám každého konkrétního člověka.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="profile-card">
          <div class="profile-card-icon" style="background:rgba(218,136,65,.1)">
            <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" style="fill:var(--clr-orange)"><path d="M12 3v10.55c-.59-.34-1.27-.55-2-.55-2.21 0-4 1.79-4 4s1.79 4 4 4 4-1.79 4-4V7h4V3h-6z"/></svg>
          </div>
          <h3>Aktivizace a trénink kognitivních funkcí</h3>
          <p>Vedla skupinové aktivity, tréninky kognitivních funkcí a reminiscenční terapii. Vytvářela koncepce aktivizačních programů, které dodnes tvoří základ každodenního programu v Domově Turovice.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="profile-card">
          <div class="profile-card-icon" style="background:rgba(75,119,171,.1)">
            <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" style="fill:var(--clr-blue)"><path d="M16 11c1.66 0 2.99-1.34 2.99-3S17.66 5 16 5c-1.66 0-3 1.34-3 3s1.34 3 3 3zm-8 0c1.66 0 2.99-1.34 2.99-3S9.66 5 8 5C6.34 5 5 6.34 5 8s1.34 3 3 3zm0 2c-2.33 0-7 1.17-7 3.5V19h14v-2.5c0-2.33-4.67-3.5-7-3.5zm8 0c-.29 0-.62.02-.97.05 1.16.84 1.97 1.97 1.97 3.45V19h6v-2.5c0-2.33-4.67-3.5-7-3.5z"/></svg>
          </div>
          <h3>Podpora rodin a krizová komunikace</h3>
